iv style=\"font-family: inherit; text-align: center\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 28px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e7 days. 4 classes.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"font-family: inherit; text-align: center\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 28px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEndless opportunities to push yourself to the finish line.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003c/tbody\u003e\n  \u003c/table\u003e\u003ctable class=\"module\" role=\"module\" data-type=\"text\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"table-layout: fixed;\" data-muid=\"eb45d24b-0c52-43db-a74a-7a14ec35c274.1\" data-mc-module-version=\"2019-10-22\"\u003e\n    \u003ctbody\u003e\n      \u003ctr\u003e\n        \u003ctd style=\"padding:30px 30px 30px 30px; line-height:30px; text-align:inherit; background-color:#000000;\" height=\"100%\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#000000\" role=\"module-content\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv style=\"font-family: inherit; text-align: center\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 30px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLet\u0027s do this! \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #cccccc; font-size: 30px; font-family: times, serif\"\u003e💪\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003c/tbody\u003e\n  \u003c/table\u003e\u003ctable border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"module\" data-role=\"module-button\" data-type=\"button\" role=\"module\" style=\"table-layout:fixed;\" width=\"100%\" data-muid=\"44e4f5d7-4879-4df2-9e06-0b9a5d5a978e\"\u003e\n      \u003ctbody\u003e\n        \u003ctr\u003e\n          \u003ctd align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#000000